drist
-----

drist is a tool to configure and synchronize configurations to servers.


Build and install
-----------------

# make install


Usage and examples
------------------

See the examples directory.


Dependencies
------------

- POSIX sh and shell utilities.
- sudo or doas (optional)
- ssh
- rsync
- POSIX make (optional)


